As one of the most dynamic sub-sections of the robotics industry collaborative robotics, aka 'cobots', have gone from an interesting novelty to a key emerging market within less than a decade. "While collaborative robots have ceased being a novelty, we expect their adoption rate to accelerate in the coming decades, going from a relative outlier in the larger industry to a central pillar," said Rian Whitton, Research Analyst at ABI Research.  "Currently less than US$500 million in global revenue in 2017, the cobot market will grow considerably -- to nearly US$13 billion in 2027. The largest markets now are in Europe and the United States, but the APAC region will be the primary source of growth for the future, largely as a reflection of China's increased adoption of robotic solutions."

Body: News Update from AITHEON Team!!  We wanted to give you an update on the happenings behind the scenes of Aitheon.  As you are well versed in crypto, you know that the process of getting on exchanges requires intensive back and forth relay of information and verification for the process to be completed and AIC to be listed on exchanges.  Likewise, we at Aitheon also want to make sure that we are on exchanges with high volume and a solid reputation for ease and safety of user. We also firmly believe that we need to be making the RIGHT moves, versus haphazardly making any available ‚Äúright now‚Äù move.  We will continue to move forward with the exchange process and expect this to be completed within the upcoming weeks. Total token allocation we expect to announce within 1-2 weeks and airdrop tokens will begin distribution soon after.  Keep in mind that in the near future major news about Aitheon will be announced. (The public announcement of the largest robotics deal that you, as our members, had private access to will take place within the next few months.)   Remember that we are all token holders and members of this community. As leaders of such, we know that our decisions impact each and every one of us and we want to make the best possible decisions.  Some exciting news-  Our first official bartending robot was purchased during the ICO by D26 Bar in Hong Kong!! The Core Team will be flying out in the upcoming weeks to install it; where it will be serving drinks at the 2018 LKF Beer and Music Festival July 21st & 22nd to an estimated crowd of 50,000 people. We couldn‚Äôt be more excited!!!!   Other types of robotics will be coming out shortly which will expand the Aitheon Platform offerings and also the visible markets to the public. We have been contracted to start automating several other small businesses including a crepery, frozen yogurt shop, a restaurant, and another bar.  Thank you all for being solid members of our community. Stay tuned for next week's newsletter where we will continue to share updates and exciting news. Also join our announcement channel at https://t.me/aitheonannouncements.    -Team Aitheon

Title: [ANN][ICO] ü§ñAitheon: DIGITAL ECOSYSTEM SIMPLIFYING YOUR WORLD w/ A.I, ROBOTICS
Body: Aitheon's model of "mining" is completely unique and it requires actual work from Specialists (miners). You could say its Proof of Performance. How it works: The A.I. is able to solve 90-99% of the tasks its been given. The rest 1-10% needs a human touch. Examples: Handwritten documents that the system cant recognize, trouble with facial recognition, Voice recognition in case someone has a heavy accent and stuff like that. So its not the typical mining where you leave your equipement do the work, in Aitheon's case its more like an actual job.

Body: Aitheon On A Globe Trotting Mission: Meetings With Leading Firms Over Their Robotics And AI Integrating Platform  Aitheon is a Blockchain based platform designed to integrate a number of robotics, AI, IoT, human specialists and cryptocurrency into one massive decentralized system. The platform acts as a service for other firms and manufacturers, who wish to utilize the data processing and integration ability of the platform for their businesses and bring down costs, increase efficiency and increase data processing capabilities.  The Aitheon platform is a unique platform and is not a concept that is just written in a whitepaper. With more than seven years of development and actual live testing of its core programming, the Blockchain platform allows firms and organizations to merge their human work element with AI to automate tasks that can become high-stress jobs due to their repetitive nature. Areas such as recruitment, data entry, logistics, autonomous vehicles and many others could be substantially improved. Author: S3cco
Title: [ANN][ICO] ü§ñAitheon: DIGITAL ECOSYSTEM SIMPLIFYING YOUR WORLD w/ A.I, ROBOTICS
Body: Bitcoin Garden: Ethereum-Based Blockchain Platform to Revolutionize Package Delivery Business https://bitcoingarden.org/ethereum-based-blockchain-platform-revolutionize-package-delivery-business/  Aitheon, the Ethereum-based platform that announced its coin presale at the North American Blockchain Conference in Miami earlier this month, is looking to revolutionize the package delivery business with their latest partnership. Aitheon is partnering up with CarSmartt, a unique ride-sharing and package delivery application, to develop, test, and launch a fleet of driverless vehicles. Aitheon will implement the same driverless technology that has been showcased in Miami, backed by the safety and reliability provided by remote ‚Äúpilots‚Äù operating on the Aitheon network.  With Aitheon working on developing and installing the driverless system, Carsmartt plans to purchase and operate a fleet of cars to deliver packages to customers, which will be controlled by the blockchain.  Aitheon plans on building and testing at least 5 of their driverless vehicles in 2018 at the CarSmartt production facility in Nevada. They are currently working on integrating the CarSmartt application into the Aitheon platform, a phase they plan to complete in the next 4 months. The vehicle testing phase is scheduled to commence later in summer this year.  Aitheon will bring in the hardware and software technology through partnerships with Quanergy, the leading provider of solid-state LIDAR sensors and smart sensing solutions and Nvidia Driveworks, a leader in advanced automotive technologies, to operate the driverless vehicles around the clock. The final testing of the vehicles will be done in Italy; Aitheon and CarSmartt expect to produce around 5 to 10 cars per month....
